#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.0.rst:2
msgid "r3.0.0"
msgstr "r3.0.0"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.0.rst:4
msgid "🎯 Revolutionary Visual Design"
msgstr "🎯 革命性的可视化设计"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.0.rst:6
msgid ""
"**Drag-and-Drop Process Designer**: No complex configuration needed. "
"Complete complex business process modeling through intuitive drag-and-"
"drop connections. Supports advanced nodes like conditional branches, "
"parallel tasks, and hooks."
msgstr "**拖拽式流程设计器**：无需复杂配置，拖拽连线即可完成复杂业务流程建模，支持条件分支、并行任务、钩子等高级节点。"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.0.rst:7
msgid ""
"**Smart Form Designer**: Powerful visual form building tool with rich "
"field types (text, numbers, dropdowns, personnel selection, attachments, "
"etc.) and flexible layouts."
msgstr "**智能表单设计器**：可视化表单搭建，字段类型丰富（文本、数字、下拉、人员选择、附件等），布局灵活。"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.0.rst:8
msgid ""
"**Real-time Preview & Validation**: Real-time preview during process "
"design with built-in process logic validation to prevent design errors "
"early."
msgstr "**实时预览与校验**：流程设计时实时预览，内置流程逻辑校验，提前避免设计错误。"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.0.rst:9
msgid ""
"**Multi-Version Process Configuration**: You can configure multiple "
"versions of processes and easily test and switch between versions."
msgstr "**多版本流程配置**：可配置多个流程版本，便于测试与版本切换。"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.0.rst:12
msgid "🔧 Ultimate Flexibility & Extensibility"
msgstr "🔧 极致灵活与可扩展性"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.0.rst:14
msgid ""
"**Plugin Architecture**: We provide plugin extension capabilities for "
"almost all key nodes (such as custom actions, permission validation, "
"notification methods, etc.). Your unique business logic can be easily "
"integrated like building blocks."
msgstr "**插件化架构**：几乎所有关键节点（自定义操作、权限校验、通知方式等）均支持插件扩展，像搭积木一样接入你的业务逻辑。"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.0.rst:15
msgid ""
"**Powerful API System**: Provides comprehensive and clear RESTful APIs "
"for seamless integration with your customer service systems, CMDB, "
"monitoring systems, CI/CD, OA, and other third-party systems."
msgstr "**强大的 API 体系**：提供完善清晰的 RESTful API，可无缝对接客服系统、CMDB、监控、CI/CD、OA 等第三方系统。"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.0.rst:16
msgid ""
"**Highly Customizable Permission Model**: Supports fine-grained "
"permission control based on roles, departments, or even specific business"
" conditions to meet complex enterprise permission management needs."
msgstr "**高度可定制的权限模型**：支持按角色、部门甚至业务条件做细粒度权限控制，满足复杂的企业权限管理需求。"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.0.rst:18
msgid "💼 Enterprise-Ready Features Out of the Box"
msgstr "💼 开箱即用的企业级特性"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.0.rst:20
msgid ""
"**Multi-Type Ticket Support**: Easily manage various processes including "
"IT operations, HR approvals, financial reimbursements, customer service, "
"etc."
msgstr "**多类型工单支持**：可轻松管理运维、HR 审批、费用报销、客服等各类流程。"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.0.rst:21
msgid ""
"**Automation & Smart Routing**: Supports conditional routing based on "
"form data, automatic assignee assignment, and intelligent ticket flow."
msgstr "**自动化与智能路由**：支持基于表单数据的条件路由、自动分派处理人及智能流转。"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.0.rst:22
msgid ""
"**Comprehensive Audit Logs**: Complete records of every operation from "
"ticket creation to closure, meeting compliance and audit requirements."
msgstr "**完备的审计日志**：记录从工单创建到关闭的每一步操作，满足合规与审计要求。"

#: ../../source/others/release_notes/r3.x/r3.0.0.rst:23
msgid ""
"**Multi-Tenant Support (Optional)**: Provides data isolation capabilities"
" for SaaS providers or large enterprise groups (requires additional "
"authorization)."
msgstr "**多租户支持（可选）**：提供数据隔离能力，适用于 SaaS 服务商或大型企业集团（需额外授权）。"
